FBIS4-13809 "drnes079_l_94006" FBIS-NES-94-079 Daily Report 24 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Peres' Bureau Denies Differences With Rabin Peres' Bureau Denies Differences With Rabin TA2404132194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1300 GMT 24 Apr 94 TA2404132194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres' bureau announced that there is total agreement between Mr. Peres and Prime Minister Yitzhaq Rabin on the tactics and path to be taken in the negotiations with the PLO. Our correspondent Hayim Hecht reports that this was said in response to the report that there are differences of opinion between the two on the negotiations with the Palestinians, which are focused on the issue of whether Israel must sign an agreement within two weeks.
